1. *Okolo* jezera je bila lepa šuma. (Around the lake there was a beautiful forest.)
2. *Okolo* je bilo puno ljudi. (There were a lot of people around.)
3. Ja sam šetala *okolo* i uživala u lepoti. (I was walking around and enjoying the beauty.)
4. Njegov stan je bio *okolo* tri sata vožnje od moje kuće. (His apartment was around three hours drive from my house.)
5. *Okolo* se zalepio za nju. (He stuck around her.)